INSERT INTO `models` VALUES ('BMW Z3',7148,'coil-on-plug',1795,'130d96fb-db1d-43bb-8da8-0106efefde89','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','06cdf0c5-38bc-4141-a35e-c43468c64c33','0afc012f-f95b-454f-bbc0-9fa4ac1d7c03',1995,5.6,'../static/images/bmw_z3.jpg','The BMW Z3 is a compact two-seater sports car that was produced from 1995 to 2002. It was BMW\'s first mass-produced roadster and gained widespread popularity, in part due to its appearance in the James Bond film \"GoldenEye.\" The Z3 features a classic long-hood, short-deck design and was available with a variety of inline-four and inline-six engines, offering a blend of sporty performance and open-air driving pleasure.','BMW'),('BMW XM',178239,'coil-on-plug',4395,'61f7b7c8-ae84-492a-9539-447aea0ab72d','dca5082a-155f-4c08-a596-2b64978ce9c3','06cdf0c5-38bc-4141-a35e-c43468c64c33','11f8f7d9-9f8a-4950-91f2-a6dbf0b2e37a',2025,4.1,'../static/images/bmw_xm.jpg','The BMW XM is a luxury plug-in hybrid SUV that combines a 4.4-liter V8 engine with an electric motor, delivering a total output of 644 horsepower. It offers a spacious interior, advanced technology features, and the performance expected from BMW\'s M division. The XM represents BMW\'s commitment to blending high performance with electrification in the SUV segment.','BMW'),('Aston Martin Rapide',172760,'coil-on-plug',5935,'130d96fb-db1d-43bb-8da8-0106efefde89','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','dea30080-e827-454c-9b44-23fbd9f796ea','13f62e68-b5fd-40b1-9fcd-b95c624685ef',2020,4.2,'../static/images/aston_martin_rapide.jpg','The Aston Martin Rapide is a high-performance luxury sedan designed to combine the elegance of a grand tourer with the practicality of a four-door car. It is powered by a naturally aspirated 5.9-liter V12 engine producing up to 580 horsepower in the high-performance Rapide AMR variant. The interior features hand-crafted materials, luxurious seating for four, and an advanced infotainment system. The Rapide maintains Aston Martin’s signature styling while delivering an engaging driving experience.','Aston Martin'),('Aston Martin DBX',173270,'coil-on-plug',3982,'130d96fb-db1d-43bb-8da8-0106efefde89','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','dea30080-e827-454c-9b44-23fbd9f796ea','175938bd-93e5-4df3-b984-3d8005f462c8',2025,3.1,'../static/images/aston_martin_dbx.jpg','The Aston Martin DBX is the brand\'s inaugural luxury SUV, blending performance with versatility. It is powered by a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine producing 697 horsepower and 663 lb-ft of torque, enabling a 0-60 mph acceleration in approximately 3.1 seconds. The DBX offers a spacious interior with seating for five, advanced technology features, and a cargo capacity of 24.5 cubic feet. Its design reflects Aston Martin\'s signature elegance, making it a standout in the luxury SUV market.','Aston Martin'),('Aston Martin Vanquish',333663,'coil-on-plug',5204,'130d96fb-db1d-43bb-8da8-0106efefde89','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','dea30080-e827-454c-9b44-23fbd9f796ea','1795a4c6-b6c1-4322-9fac-fdf559123c36',2025,3.3,'../static/images/aston_martin_vanquish.jpg','The Aston Martin Vanquish is a grand tourer that combines luxury with high performance. It is powered by a 5.2-liter twin-turbocharged V12 engine producing 835 PS (approximately 824 horsepower) and 1000 Nm of torque, allowing it to accelerate from 0 to 62 mph in 3.3 seconds and reach a top speed of 214 mph (345 km/h). The Vanquish features a commanding and sophisticated design, with a front mid-mounted engine driving the rear wheels. The interior is crafted with high-quality materials, offering a blend of elegance and advanced technology. \n','Aston Martin'),('Bentley Bentayga',168967,'coil-on-plug',3996,'61f7b7c8-ae84-492a-9539-447aea0ab72d','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','982ef209-f1fb-4f5b-b309-b4f701756df3','24cebc76-95f2-41e8-aaf9-194376e8681d',2015,4.5,'../static/images/bentley_bentayga.jpg',' The Bentley Bentayga is a luxury SUV that combines exceptional performance with unparalleled craftsmanship. Introduced in 2015, it offers a range of powertrains, including a 4.0-liter V8 petrol engine producing 542 horsepower, a 6.0-liter W12 petrol engine, and a 3.0-liter hybrid option. The V8 variant accelerates from 0 to 60 mph in approximately 4.5 seconds. The Bentayga\'s interior features exquisite materials and advanced technology, providing a comfortable and sophisticated driving experience. Its exterior design exudes presence and elegance, making it a standout in the luxury SUV segment. ​','Bentley'),('Aston Martin Vantage',160872,'coil-on-plug',3982,'130d96fb-db1d-43bb-8da8-0106efefde89','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','dea30080-e827-454c-9b44-23fbd9f796ea','26907120-e29b-4775-bd4f-41ae1f67bff2',2025,3.4,'../static/images/aston_martin_vantage.jpg',' The Aston Martin Vantage is a high-performance sports car that seamlessly blends luxury with exhilarating driving dynamics. Equipped with a 4.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine producing 665 horsepower and 590 lb-ft of torque, the Vantage accelerates from 0 to 60 mph in approximately 3.4 seconds and reaches a top speed of 202 mph. Its design features aggressive styling cues, a wider rear track, and aerodynamic enhancements. Inside, the Vantage offers a driver-focused cockpit with premium materials, advanced infotainment systems, and customizable options to suit individual preferences. This model continues Aston Martin\'s legacy of crafting vehicles that deliver both luxury and performance. \n','Aston Martin'),('BMW Z4',48468,'coil-on-plug',1998,'130d96fb-db1d-43bb-8da8-0106efefde89','dca5082a-155f-4c08-a596-2b64978ce9c3','06cdf0c5-38bc-4141-a35e-c43468c64c33','2cd89895-a555-4b8b-a072-38490ad746b7',2025,5.2,'../static/images/bmw_z4.jpg',' The BMW Z4 is a two-seat roadster that combines classic sports car aesthetics with modern performance and technology. The 2025 model features a retractable soft top, a choice of turbocharged engines, and a driver-focused interior, offering an exhilarating open-air driving experience.','BMW'),('Bentley Mulsanne',185182,'coil-on-plug',6752,'e9e81084-b7ee-47fa-80e5-0055142d2170','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','982ef209-f1fb-4f5b-b309-b4f701756df3','2fc1f288-a1da-433d-b452-35409df66699',2010,5.1,'../static/images/bentley_mulsanne.jpg','The Bentley Mulsanne is a luxury sedan that epitomizes British elegance and performance. Produced between 2010 and 2020, it was powered by a 6.75-liter twin-turbocharged V8 engine, delivering 505 horsepower and 752 lb-ft of torque in the standard model. The Mulsanne Speed variant offered enhanced performance with 530 horsepower and 811 lb-ft of torque, achieving a 0-60 mph time of approximately 4.9 seconds. ','Bentley'),('BMW 2-Series',35752,'coil-on-plug',1998,'ee6895c9-7a41-4ad7-840a-4436198d811a','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','06cdf0c5-38bc-4141-a35e-c43468c64c33','37384584-41b8-4776-9bd2-72b767955ea2',2024,5.5,'../static/images/bmw_2_series.jpg','The BMW 2 Series is a compact luxury vehicle offering both coupe and gran coupe (sedan) body styles. Renowned for its dynamic performance, precise handling, and upscale interior, the 2 Series blends sporty aesthetics with advanced technology. The 2024 model continues BMW\'s tradition of delivering an engaging driving experience in a stylish and compact package.​','BMW'),('BYD Seal',44690,'electric motor',0,'e9e81084-b7ee-47fa-80e5-0055142d2170','1a5029c9-a78c-4f4b-89f1-82d909887884','49632c36-bc09-4623-88e1-878b80116959','3745bfe0-f6be-498f-a577-cd59f40f73a3',2022,3.8,'../static/images/byd_seal.jpg','The BYD Seal is a sleek electric sedan built on BYD\'s e-Platform 3.0, designed exclusively for pure electric vehicles. It offers both rear-wheel-drive and all-wheel-drive configurations, with power outputs ranging from 150 kW to 390 kW. Equipped with BYD\'s Blade Battery technology, the Seal provides a range of up to 570 km (approximately 354 miles) on the WLTP cycle. Notable features include a 15.6-inch rotating 