erior and aerodynamic enhancements. ','Aston Martin'),('Abarth Punto Evo',16689.91,'coil-on-plug',1368,'7d651926-c178-4614-a0df-d5a6c472ddb4','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','b2ca342f-9267-438f-bf7b-861bf87f4c64','ef50094c-f0e0-4d98-8c59-49a2a176d004',2010,7.6,'../static/images/abarth_punto_evo.jpg','The Abarth Punto Evo is a performance-enhanced version of the Fiat Punto, developed by Abarth to offer a sporty driving experience. It features a turbocharged 1.4-liter MultiAir engine producing 162 horsepower, sport-tuned suspension, and distinctive Abarth styling elements, providing a dynamic yet practical ride.','Abarth'),('Bentley Arnage',119229.66,'coil-on-plug',6750,'130d96fb-db1d-43bb-8da8-0106efefde89','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','982ef209-f1fb-4f5b-b309-b4f701756df3','f1ccf1c4-6c14-4b35-bd7d-cf6b0f0569c3',1998,5.5,'../static/images/bentley_arnage.jpg','The Bentley Arnage is a full-size luxury sedan produced from 1998 to 2010. Initially powered by a 4.4-liter BMW V8 engine, it later transitioned to Bentley\'s traditional 6.75-liter V8, offering enhanced performance. The Arnage T variant, introduced in 2002, featured twin turbochargers, producing 507 horsepower and achieving 0-60 mph in approximately 5.5 seconds. Renowned for its handcrafted interior, the Arnage combined classic British luxury with modern engineering, solidifying its status as a distinguished vehicle in the luxury car segment.','Bentley'),('Alpine A110',47691.86,'coil-on-plug',1798,'9f17bfa8-aa44-41aa-b08f-3c6101302502','abd6727c-5148-4c7c-8252-40c404059633','0228e5aa-4f2b-4aac-a849-8b458865cc5d','f4b2b027-d0db-4185-8cec-386ad1e76d8c',2017,4.2,'../static/images/alpine_a110.jpg','The Alpine A110 is a lightweight sports coupe that pays homage to the original A110 \"Berlinette\" from the 1960s and 70s. Featuring a mid-mounted 1.8-liter turbocharged inline-four engine, it delivers between 252 and 300 horsepower, depending on the variant. The A110\'s lightweight construction, weighin